OL,6,FJust over 120 have been reviewed so
OL,7,Ffar and HCS Medical Director Patrick
OL,8,FArmstrong believes "probably between
OL,9,F40 and 50" will be referred to the
OL,10,FViscount.
OL,12,F'Dr Y' is still on the payroll but not
OL,13,Fcurrently practising in Jersey while
OL,14,F'Dr Z' left the island some time ago.
OL,16,FA separate audit also highlighted
OL,17,F"significant concerns" over the
OL,18,Fmedication given by these doctors to
OL,19,Fpatients between January 2019 and
OL,20,FJanuary 2022.
