OL,6,FIt found there was no appropriate
OL,7,Fevidence for 153 people to be given
OL,8,Fanti-rheumatic and anti-inflammation
OL,9,Fdrugs - more than half of all the
OL,10,Frecords reviewed.
OL,12,FIn 38% of cases, these prescriptions
OL,13,Fwere then stopped following face-to-
OL,14,Fface appointments.
OL,16,FMr Armstrong says assessments by
OL,17,Findependent specialists have so far
OL,18,Frevealed that 33 living patients may
OL,19,Fhave been harmed by their diagnosis,
OL,20,Ftreatment and care under these two
OL,21,Fdoctors.
