OL,4,Cpatient deaths referred to Coroner
OL,6,FThey have been given an apology and
OL,7,Fcompensation will be offered, he hopes
OL,8,Flater this year, either on a case-by-
OL,9,Fcase basis or through a general scheme.
OL,11,FIt follows a damning independent
OL,12,Freport published earlier this year
OL,13,Fwhich found that the standard of
OL,14,Frheumatology care in Jersey was "well
OL,15,Fbelow what the review team would
OL,16,Fconsider acceptable".
