OL,6,FAt the time, HCS admitted it is
OL,7,F"inevitable" that some patients "will
OL,8,Fhave been harmed clinically,
OL,9,Femotionally or economically by their
OL,10,Fearlier diagnosis or treatment".
OL,12,FThe investigation by the Royal College
OL,13,Fof Physicians had been triggered by
OL,14,Fconcerns from locum doctors over
OL,15,Frecord-keeping, case management and
OL,16,Fcommunication.
