OL,6,FMr Armstrong adds: "I would like to
OL,7,Freassure patients of the Rheumatology
OL,8,FService that the recommendations made
OL,9,Fby the Royal College for improvements
OL,10,Fto the services are progressing well.
OL,12,F"Of the 26 recommendations made, 16
OL,13,Fhave been fully implemented and the
OL,14,Fremaining 10 are well on the way to
OL,15,Fbeing implemented."
OL,17,FHe also explains that progress is
OL,18,Fbeing made to enrol Jersey into
OL,19,Fnational audits.
